'''2013年基辅警民冲突'''指的是[[乌克兰亲欧盟示威运动|乌克兰亲欧盟示威运动]]（{{lang-uk|Євромайдан}}）期间，2013年11月30日起在[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]首都[[基辅|基辅]]发生的[[警民冲突|警民冲突]]。当天凌晨，[[别尔库特部队|别尔库特部队]]试图驱逐正在基辅[[独立广场_(基辅)|独立广场]]集会的抗议者，被广泛报道滥用暴力、殴打示威者甚至其余民众，造成79人受伤，随后独立广场被清空。第二天（12月1日）基辅市内的亲欧盟示威者无视法院禁令，重新占领独立广场和基辅市中心区的多个要道，并于下午开始冲击多处国家机关，再与警方发生冲突，使100名警员受伤。冲突后，基辅市警察局长瓦列里·科里亚克宣布负责并请辞，但乌克兰反对派认为是时任乌克兰总统[[维克多·亚努科维奇|维克多·亚努科维奇]]下令清场。冲突为亚努科维奇总统等多国政治人物所谴责，使11月21日开始的示威活动愈发激烈，并成为之后的许多人加入持续数月的示威活动的主要理由。

== 背景 ==
{{Further|乌克兰亲欧盟示威运动年表}}
2013年11月21日，乌克兰政府宣布延缓与[[欧洲联盟|欧洲联盟]]签订{{link-en|欧洲联盟联系国协定|European Union Association Agreement|联系国协定}}，转而接近[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]<ref name="人民网20131122">{{cite news |url=http://world.people.com.cn/n/2013/1122/c1002-23619418.html |title=乌克兰暂停与欧盟签署联系国协定 普京表态愿意对话 |publisher=[[人民网|人民网]] |date=2013-11-22 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |author=刘旭 |location=[[莫斯科|莫斯科]] |language=zh-cn |archive-date=2014-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322001854/http://world.people.com.cn/n/2013/1122/c1002-23619418.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ukraine drops EU plans and looks to Russia|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/11/ukraine-drops-eu-plans-looks-russia-20131121145417227621.html|publisher=[[半岛电视台英语频道|半岛电视台英语频道]]|language=en|accessdate=2014-03-28|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620030747/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/11/ukraine-drops-eu-plans-looks-russia-20131121145417227621.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，引发亲欧民众不满。当晚民众开始在[[独立广场_(基辅)|独立广场]]集会<ref>{{cite news |url=http://epaper.qingdaonews.com/html/qdrb/20131123/qdrb653276.html |title=乌克兰民众示威支持乌欧一体化 |publisher=[[青岛日报|青岛日报]] |date=2013-11-23 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |language=zh-cn |archive-date=2020-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626135014/http://epaper.qingdaonews.com/html/qdrb/20131123/qdrb653276.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Ukraine Opposition Protests Europe U-Turn |url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/business/article/ukraine-opposition-protests-europe-u-turn/490110.html |newspaper=莫斯科时报 |date=2013-11-22 |quote=Protesters gathered in the center of Kiev on Thursday night, ... Various estimates placed the crowd at the Ukrainian capital's Independence Square between 1,000 and 2,000 people, Interfax reported. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125134601/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/business/article/ukraine-opposition-protests-europe-u-turn/490110.html |archivedate=2014-01-25 |language=en |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2014-03-29 }}</ref>。

随后的几天，基辅市一直有示威活动发生，其中规模较大者发生于11月24日，即本次冲突的上一个周日，估计有5万到20万人参加<ref name=moscowtimes25>{{cite news |last=Sukhov |first=Oleg |title=Ukrainian Protests Compared to 2004 Orange Revolution |url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/ukrainian-protests-compared-to-2004-orange-revolution/490205.html |newspaper=[[莫斯科时报|莫斯科时报]] |date=2013-11-25 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122123715/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/ukrainian-protests-compared-to-2004-orange-revolution/490205.html |archivedate=2014-01-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。抗议者向独立广场<ref name="大纪元20131125">{{cite news | url=http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/11/25/n4018663.htm?photo=2 | title=数万乌克兰人抗议政府亲俄 拖延入欧协定 | work=[[大纪元时报|大纪元]] | date=2013-11-25 | accessdate=2014-03-21 | author=万平 | language=zh-cn | quote=警察星期日（24日）使用催泪瓦斯和警棍，制止一些示威者试图冲进政府大楼。示威人群举着乌克兰旗帜和欧盟旗帜，高呼口号“乌克兰属于欧洲”，并唱着国歌朝着独立广场前进。 | archive-date=2014-03-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322001700/http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/13/11/25/n4018663.htm?photo=2 | dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[欧洲广场_(基辅)|欧洲广场]]<ref>{{cite news |author=Maria Danilova |url=http://www.thestar.com/news/world/2013/11/24/ukraine_50000_rally_in_kyiv_calling_on_ukraines_government_to_sign_eu_deal_and_turn_away_from_russia.html |title=Ukraine: 50,000 rally in Kyiv calling on Ukraine's government to sign EU deal and turn away from Russia |publisher=马来西亚星报 |date=2013-11-24 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202230607/http://www.thestar.com/news/world/2013/11/24/ukraine_50000_rally_in_kyiv_calling_on_ukraines_government_to_sign_eu_deal_and_turn_away_from_russia.html |archivedate=2013-12-02 |quote=The pro-EU demonstrators, carrying giant Ukrainian and EU flags, chanted “Ukraine is Europe” and sang the national anthem as they marched toward European Square for the rally. |deadurl=yes }}</ref>两处集中，并在政府大楼前与警方发生冲突，双方使用了[[催泪弹|催泪弹]]等武器<ref name="大纪元20131125" /><ref>{{cite news |title=Mass rallies in Ukraine against government U-turn on EU |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/11/24/uk-ukraine-eu-idUKBRE9AN0C920131124 |date=2013-11-24 |agency=[[路透社|路透社]] |accessdate=2014-03-21 |language=en |quote=Riot police and an angry group of demonstrators clashed in front of government headquarters, spraying each other with pepper gas and fighting with batons, |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125153827/http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/11/24/uk-ukraine-eu-idUKBRE9AN0C920131124 |archivedate=2014-01-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Ukraine police clash with pro-EU protesters |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/11/ukraine-police-clash-with-pro-eu-protesters-20131124142743878664.html |publisher=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]] |date=2013-11-24 |quote=However, some protesters on Sunday tried to storm government buildings and police responded by using tear gas and batons against them. |accessdate=2014-03-21 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140127183154/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/europe/2013/11/ukraine-police-clash-with-pro-eu-protesters-20131124142743878664.html |archivedate=2014-01-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

11月29日由于乌克兰没有在欧盟[[东部伙伴关系|东部伙伴关系]]峰会上签订联系国协定<ref>{{cite news | url=http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2013-11/4616463.html | title=欧盟峰会未能拉住乌克兰 俄与欧盟拉力赛将继续 | work=[[环球时报|环球时报]] | date=2013-11-30 | accessdate=2014-03-26 | author=丁飞 候涛 | location=俄罗斯 | language=zh-cn | archive-date=2018-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005143046/http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2013-11/4616463.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=NSEN291113>{{cite news|url=http://www.euronews.com/2013/11/29/ukraine-fails-to-sign-landmark-deal-at-eu-summit/|title=Ukraine fails to sign landmark deal at EU summit|publisher=[[欧洲新闻台|欧洲新闻台]]|date=2013-11-29|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2020-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200413190006/https://www.euronews.com/2013/11/29/ukraine-fails-to-sign-landmark-deal-at-eu-summit|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亲欧盟示威者继续在独立广场集会，惟欧洲广场当天被亲俄罗斯抗议者占领。<ref name="基辅邮报20131129">{{cite web | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-in-ukraine-nov-29-coverage-332729.html | title=EuroMaidan rallies in Ukraine - Nov. 29 coverage | publisher=基辅邮报 | date=2013-12-01 | accessdate=2014-03-26 | language=en | archive-date=2015-11-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121154606/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-in-ukraine-nov-29-coverage-332729.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=ENBEU291113>{{cite news |url=http://www.euronews.com/2013/11/29/ukraine-s-rejection-of-eu-deal-brings-rival-rallies-at-home/ |title=Ukraine's rejection of EU deal brings rival rallies at home |publisher=[[欧洲新闻台|欧洲新闻台]] |date=2013-11-29 |accessdate=2014-03-26 |language=en |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726114705/https://www.euronews.com/2013/11/29/ukraine-s-rejection-of-eu-deal-brings-rival-rallies-at-home |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="欧洲新闻台20131129">{{cite news |url=http://www.euronews.com/2013/11/29/ukraine-tension-in-kyiv-as-pro-and-anti-government-protesters-hold-rallies/ |title=Ukraine: tension in Kyiv as pro and anti government protesters hold rallies |publisher=欧洲新闻台 |date=2013-11-29 |accessdate=2014-03-26 |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813143241/https://www.euronews.com/2013/11/29/ukraine-tension-in-kyiv-as-pro-and-anti-government-protesters-hold-rallies |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 过程 ==
在冲突前一天，11月29日便有消息称约1万名警察包围了独立广场并准备清除示威者<ref name="基辅邮报20131129" />，之后又有消息称几千名防暴警察出现在总统府附近执行保卫<ref name="基辅邮报20131129" />。同一天，乌克兰总检察长在[[哈尔科夫|哈尔科夫]]放出的一份简短声明中表示：“不会驱散和平示威者”<ref name="基辅邮报20131130c">{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/police-protesters-provoked-violence-332690.html |title=Police say protesters provoked violence (VIDEO) |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |author=Katya Gorchinskaya, Mariia Shamota |location=乌克兰 |language=en |quote=On Nov. 29 the Prosecutor General said at a briefing in Kharkiv that “there will be no dispersals of peaceful demonstrations.” |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131130115959/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/police-protesters-provoked-violence-332690.html |archivedate=2013-11-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。当晚独立广场约有1万人进行抗议活动<ref name="基辅邮报20131130f">{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/diplomats-condemn-attacks-on-euromaidan-protestors-in-kyiv-332685.html |title=Police attack on Kyiv's EuroMaidan demonstrators draws international outrage (UPDATES) |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |author=Christopher J. Miller |location=基辅 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322011121/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/diplomats-condemn-attacks-on-euromaidan-protestors-in-kyiv-332685.html |archivedate=2014-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，有约700人在独立广场过夜，其中大部分是学生<ref name="基辅邮报20131130b">{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/back-to-the-middle-ages-on-the-way-to-europe-beaten-kyiv-protesters-take-refuge-in-ancient-church-yard-332719.html |title=Back to the Middle Ages on the way to Europe: Beaten Kyiv protesters take refuge in ancient church yard |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |language=en |location=基辅 |last=Shevchenko |first=Daryna |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322010857/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/back-to-the-middle-ages-on-the-way-to-europe-beaten-kyiv-protesters-take-refuge-in-ancient-church-yard-332719.html |archivedate=2014-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

