凌晨约4:30{{NoteTag|关于警方开始行动的时间多为媒体估计值，另有目击者称是3:30<ref name="基辅邮报20131130d" />。}}（[[UTC|UTC]]+2），携有[[警棍|警棍]]、[[闪光弹|闪光弹]]和催泪瓦斯的别尔库特部队开始进入独立广场，手机信号当时亦被切断<ref name="RT20131130">{{cite news |title=Ukrainian police oust pro-EU protest from landmark Kiev square |url=http://rt.com/news/ukraine-police-disperse-protest-509/ |publisher=[[今日俄罗斯|今日俄罗斯]] |location=俄罗斯 |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221163626/http://rt.com/news/ukraine-police-disperse-protest-509/ |archivedate=2014-02-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，当时现场约有千人，主要是学生<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2013/11/131130_ukraine_clash.shtml |title=烏克蘭警方強力驅趕基輔示威者 |work=BBC中文网 |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2014-03-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131201125646/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/world/2013/11/131130_ukraine_clash.shtml |archivedate=2013-12-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。现场目击者和多家[[新闻社|新闻社]]报道称警察对民众使用了暴力<ref name="基辅邮报20131130a" />，其中{{link-en|基辅邮报|Kyiv Post}}称：“这次事件是近期乌克兰最露骨且重大的非致命警方暴行”<ref name="基辅邮报20131130a" />。一名[[丹麦|丹麦]]自由记者拍摄到了警察打人的画面，随后其本人也遭到殴打<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/police-were-like-a-machine-cleaning-the-street-says-beating-victim-332677.html |title=Police 'were like a machine cleaning the street,' says beating victim |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |last=Bonner |first=Brian |location=基辅 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322011136/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/police-were-like-a-machine-cleaning-the-street-says-beating-victim-332677.html |archivedate=2014-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。一些示威者手脚骨折，受脑震荡以及外伤，另有人失踪<ref name="基辅邮报20131130b" />，此外，亦有多名非示威者遭殴打，对此基辅邮报在报道中认为：“昨晚只是呆在独立广场周围的哪一个地方都很危险——甚至是那些没有参与当下亲欧盟示威的人。警察似乎意在殴打视线中的任何人”<ref name="基辅邮报20131130d">{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine-abroad/witness-steps-on-independence-square-were-all-covered-in-blood-332681.html |title=Victims describe excessive, indiscriminate attacks (UPDATES) |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-11-30 |accessdate=2014-03-28 |author=Daryna Shevchenko, Oksana Grytsenko |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322173746/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine-abroad/witness-steps-on-independence-square-were-all-covered-in-blood-332681.html |archivedate=2014-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。一些伤者被送往[[圣米迦勒金顶修道院|圣米迦勒金顶修道院]]<ref name="基辅邮报20131130b" />。在冲突中，抗议者以石子回击警方<ref name="基辅邮报20131130a" />。随后人们开始前往附近的圣米迦勒广场（St. Michael's Square）继续示威活动，到中午此地已聚集约4000人<ref name="基辅邮报20131130a" />。警方随后赶到该地，虽有抗议者攻击了警方车辆，但没有冲突发生<ref name="基辅邮报20131130a" />。多名反对派政治家和10个国家的大使也出现在圣米迦勒广场<ref name="基辅邮报20131130a" />。据非官方估计，当天晚上圣米迦勒广场已聚集1万人<ref name="基辅邮报20131130b" />。

乌克兰内务部在一份声明中表示：“别尔库特部队的行为是在示威者有抵抗行为之后做出的，示威者向警察扔垃圾、玻璃、水壶和着火的木棍”，并表示共有35人因流氓行为和抵抗警察而遭逮捕，不过在文书工作结束后的隔天早上就予以释放。此外，内务部还称市政部门的工作人员向其抱怨，说独立广场的装饰工作无法正常进行，警方也在一份声明中表示：“市政工人要求首都警察保证其车辆安全进入独立广场”。<ref name="基辅邮报20131130b" />

基辅城市医疗服务的外科主任表示，有35人在24小时间寻求医治，大部分伤为擦伤<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/kyiv-chief-doctor-some-35-people-seek-help-from-doctors-seven-hospitalized-after-violent-dispersal-of-opposition-rally-332701.html |title=Kyiv chief doctor: Some 35 people seek help from doctors, seven hospitalized after violent dispersal of opposition rally |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-11-30 |agency=Interfax-Ukraine |accessdate=2014-03-28 |location=乌克兰 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122003217/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/kyiv-chief-doctor-some-35-people-seek-help-from-doctors-seven-hospitalized-after-violent-dispersal-of-opposition-rally-332701.html |archivedate=2014-01-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。几天后，乌克兰副检察长表示，共有79人在11月30日的冲突中受伤，其中有6名学生、4名记者和2名外国人，另有7名警察受伤<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/75-were-injured-during-nov-30-dispersal-of-euromaidan-333103.html |title=75 were injured during Nov. 30 dispersal of EuroMaidan |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-12-05 |agency=Interfax-Ukraine |accessdate=2014-03-28 |location=乌克兰 |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104210623/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/75-were-injured-during-nov-30-dispersal-of-euromaidan-333103.html |archivedate=2014-01-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。伤者中包括一名[[路透社|路透社]]记者<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.takungpao.com/paper/q/2013/1201/2075339.html | title=乌万人示威爆冲突数十伤 | work=大公报 | date=2013-12-01 | accessdate=2014-03-29 | language=zh-cn | archive-date=2020-06-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626135141/http://news.takungpao.com/paper/q/2013/1201/2075339.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 余波 ==
[[File:Riot_police_(Bekrut),_defending_the_Kiev_city_council_building,_and_protesters_clash_at_Bankova_str,_Kiev,_Ukraine._December_1,_2013-2.jpg|thumbnail]]

冲突的第二天，12月1日民众掀起新一轮大规模抗议示威，要求总统亚努科维奇下台并号召举行全国[[罢工|大罢工]]<ref name="北京日报20131202">{{cite news| url=http://bjrb.bjd.com.cn/html/2013-12/02/content_130243.htm| title=乌克兰国家机关遭抗议者冲击| work=[[北京日报|北京日报]]| date=2013-12-02| agency=新华社| accessdate=2014-03-29| location=基辅| language=zh-cn| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140329114155/http://bjrb.bjd.com.cn/html/2013-12/02/content_130243.htm| archivedate=2014-03-29}}</ref>。凌晨便有报道称一些人在圣米迦勒广场教授抗议者如何自卫<ref name="基辅邮报20131201a">{{cite web | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-12-am-to-2-pm-euromaidan-rallies-in-ukraine-332752.html | title=EuroMaidan rallies on Dec. 1. The peaceful morning | work=基辅邮报 | date=2013-12-01 | accessdate=2014-03-30 | language=en | archive-date=2015-11-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121141432/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-12-am-to-2-pm-euromaidan-rallies-in-ukraine-332752.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。尽管基辅市法院当天宣布自12月1日到1月7日禁止在独立广场、欧洲广场、总统办公厅和内政部大楼进行示威活动<ref name="基辅邮报20131201a" />，早晨，示威者还是在一个公园集合并向独立广场前进<ref name="BBC中文网20131201" />，于中午突破警方设置的路障进入广场，在其中展开巨幅[[欧盟旗帜|欧盟旗帜]]并将[[乌克兰国旗|乌克兰国旗]]并排展示<ref name="北京日报20131202" />。一些正在独立广场的圣诞树上工作的市政工人逃离，留下了其车辆<ref name="基辅邮报20131201a" />。几小时后即有报道称独立广场已见不到警察，唯有数目仍在增多的抗议者<ref name="基辅邮报20131201a" />。此外抗议者还占领了舍甫琴科广场等市中心的其他地方<ref name="基辅邮报20131201a" />。一个公民权利组织在中午估计约有20万人占领了基辅市内的要道，包括独立广场、圣米迦勒广场、[[赫雷夏蒂克街|赫雷夏蒂克街]]等<ref name="基辅邮报20131201a" />。

下午，抗议者开始从独立广场离开，沿着班科夫街（通向总统办公厅和内阁建筑）、赫雷夏蒂克街（通向基辅市政厅）等<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a">{{cite web |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-a-rowdy-afternoon-332780.html |title=EuroMaidan rallies on Dec. 1: A rowdy afternoon |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-12-02 |accessdate=2014-03-30 |language=en |archive-date=2008-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201194141/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-a-rowdy-afternoon-332780.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>前往冲击乌克兰国家机关<ref name="北京日报20131202" />。在基辅市政厅，冲入其中的人群悬挂[[乌克兰国旗|乌克兰国旗]]并高呼“乌克兰属于我们”<ref name="BBC中文网20131201">{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2013/12/131201_ukraine_kiyv_cityhall.shtml | title=乌克兰反对派冲入基辅市政厅 | work=BBC中文网 | date=2013-12-01 | agency=美联社 | accessdate=2014-03-29 | location=基辅 | archive-date=2013-12-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214114422/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2013/12/131201_ukraine_kiyv_cityhall.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在总统办公厅前，抗议者与警方发生激烈冲突，甚至有戴面具的抗议者驾驶被市政工人遗留在独立广场的[[拖拉机|拖拉机]]冲击警方设置的栅栏，一些人试图叫停他们，喊着：“只要和平行为！”<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />。警方没有试图强行驱逐抗议者，而是成排站着挡住人群<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />。抗议者把人行道上的砖块扔向警察，并用棍子敲击警察，其中不少人带着面具，警察以催泪弹回击，冲突中还能听到枪声<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />。冲突造成100名警员受伤，也有其他人受伤甚至昏厥<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />。但示威者没能突破警方封锁线<ref name="北京日报20131202" />。此外，一伙人试图驾车冲击总统府，但没有成功<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />。当晚，示威群众试图拉倒位于塔拉斯·舍甫琴科大道的基辅市最后一座[[苏联|苏联]]领导人[[弗拉基米尔·伊里奇·列宁|列宁]]的雕像，但由于警方的防守失败<ref>{{Cite web|title=EuroMaidan rallies on Dec. 1: A rowdy afternoon - Dec. 02, 2013|url=https://www.kyivpost.com/article/content/ukraine-politics/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-a-rowdy-afternoon-332780.html|accessdate=2021-04-12|date=2013-12-01|work=KyivPost|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317091012/https://www.kyivpost.com/article/content/ukraine-politics/euromaidan-rallies-on-dec-1-a-rowdy-afternoon-332780.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管如此，约300名示威者还是攻击了防暴警察，造成至少2名警察受伤<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/radical-protesters-clash-with-special-police-unit-at-lenin-monument-332772.html | title=Radical protesters clash with special police unit at Lenin monument (VIDEOS) | work=基辅邮报 | date=2013-12-01 | accessdate=2014-04-05 | author=Christopher J. Miller | location=基辅 | language=en | archive-date=2008-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201194141/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/radical-protesters-clash-with-special-police-unit-at-lenin-monument-332772.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />（一个星期后的12月8日，这座雕像终被示威者[[基辅列宁雕像倒塌事件|拉倒]]）。反对派领袖[[佩特罗·波罗申科|佩特罗·波罗申科]]估计抗议者有35万人，而反对党[[全乌克兰祖国联盟|全乌克兰祖国联盟]]估计当天一共有50万人上街游行<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />。

== 调查 ==
冲突发生当天，11月30日，时任乌克兰总统亚努科维奇便要求检查机构调查事件并迅速向他和全国汇报结果<ref name="基辅邮报20131130g" />。随后，基辅警察局长瓦列里·科里亚克（Valeriy Koryak）承认下令警方行动，并表示后悔<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/kyiv-city-police-chief-admits-ordering-attack-on-euromaidan-protestors-332714.html | title=Kyiv city police chief admits ordering attack on EuroMaidan protesters | work=基辅邮报 | date=2013-11-30 | accessdate=2014-03-30 | author=Christopher J. Miller | location=基辅 | language=en | archive-date=2015-09-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150911092258/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv/kyiv-city-police-chief-admits-ordering-attack-on-euromaidan-protestors-332714.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，之后[[#影响|宣布请辞]]。然而乌克兰反对派则指责亚努科维奇总统下令清场，例如[[阿尔谢尼·亚采纽克|阿尔谢尼·亚采纽克]]就表示有两个人应为事件负责，即“维克多·亚努科维奇作为顾客，内务部部长维塔利·扎哈尔琴科作为执行人”<ref>{{cite news | url=http://ukrainianweek.com/News/95352 | title=Ukrainian opposition calls for early elections and national strike | work=The Ukrainian Week | date=2013-11-30 | accessdate=2014-04-02 | language=en | quote=According to Yatsenyuk,  the two people in Ukraine are responsible for this crime – " Viktor Yanukovych as a customer and Minister of Interior Vitaliy Zakharchenko as a performer" | archive-date=2008-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201194141/http://ukrainianweek.com/News/95352 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

12月1日的冲突之后，乌克兰内务部称自被扣留者处得到消息，有约300名{{link-en|Bratstvo|Bratstvo}}组织（直译为“兄弟会”）成员参与了总统办公厅前的非法行为，另外，在基辅市政厅附近的行动也与一名反对党[[斯沃博达党|斯沃博达党]]的代表有关<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/police-say-over-300-radicals-led-attack-on-presidents-office-332786.html |title=Police say over 300 radicals led attack on president's office |work=基辅邮报 |date=2013-12-02 |agency=Interfax-Ukraine |accessdate=2014-04-01 |location=乌克兰 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203012112/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/ukraine/police-say-over-300-radicals-led-attack-on-presidents-office-332786.html |archivedate=2013-12-03 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
警民冲突发生后不久，11月30日乌克兰总统办公厅主任谢尔盖·里奥沃克钦（Serhiy Lyovochkin）请辞<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/politics/head-of-yanukovychs-administration-resigns-332692.html | title=Lyovochkin, Yanukovych's chief of staff, resigns | work=基辅邮报 | date=2013-11-30 | accessdate=2014-03-30 | first=Katya | last=Gorchinskaya | language=en | archive-date=2015-11-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121170726/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/politics/head-of-yanukovychs-administration-resigns-332692.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，立法议员因娜·博戈斯洛夫斯卡娅和Davyd Zhvania宣布退出[[地区党|地区党]]<ref name="基辅邮报20131130g">{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/politics/yanukovych-outraged-by-maidans-break-up-threatens-to-punish-guilty-332718.html | title=Yanukovych says police beatings not his fault | work=基辅邮报 | date=2013-11-30 | accessdate=2014-03-30 | first=Oksana | last=Grytsenko | language=en | archive-date=2015-11-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121133355/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/politics/yanukovych-outraged-by-maidans-break-up-threatens-to-punish-guilty-332718.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。之后，基辅警察局局长瓦列里·科里亚克（Valeriy Koryak）亦提出辞职<ref name="基辅邮报20131202a" />。

一些乌克兰反对派政治家被抗议者批评没有尽通知和保护的义务，反对党在冲突发生前数小时将广场上属于其的声音设备搬走，因而被一些抗议者认为已提前获知。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/politics/opposition-accused-of-failure-to-lead-public-protests-332713.html | title=Opposition under fire for failure to protect protesters | work=基辅邮报 | date=2013-11-30 | accessdate=2014-03-30 | author=Anastasia Vlasova, Christopher J. Miller, Oksana Grytsenko, Olga Rudenko | language=en | archive-date=2015-11-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121161747/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/politics/opposition-accused-of-failure-to-lead-public-protests-332713.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年12月的一份调查显示，近70%的受调查者表示其参与[[乌克兰亲欧盟示威运动|亲欧盟示威运动]]的原因便是11月30日警方暴力驱逐了抗议者<ref>{{cite web | url=http://dif.org.ua/ua/events/gvkrlgkaeths.htm | title=Майдан-2013: хто стоїть, чому і за що? | work=Ilko Kucheriv Democratic Initiatives Foundation | accessdate=2014-03-28 | language=uk | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321230349/http://dif.org.ua/ua/events/gvkrlgkaeths.htm | archivedate=2014-03-21 }}</ref>，为此[[欧洲新闻台|欧洲新闻台]]在报道中认为：“乌克兰当局以暴力驱逐和平示威者的决定是个大错误”<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.euronews.com/2013/12/13/ukrainian-opposition-uses-polls-to-bolster-cause/ | title=Ukrainian opposition uses polls to bolster cause | work=欧洲新闻台 | date=2013-12-13 | accessdate=2014-03-28 | language=en | archive-date=2014-01-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140128023135/http://www.euronews.com/2013/12/13/ukrainian-opposition-uses-polls-to-bolster-cause/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年12月14日，时任乌克兰总统亚努科维奇辞退了基辅市长奥莱克桑德·波波夫和[[乌克兰国家安全委员会|国家安全委员会]]副主任弗拉基米尔
·斯沃科维什奇，{{link-en|乌克兰总检察长|General Prosecutor of Ukraine|}}称其原因是“在11月30日越权要求警方行动”。此外，基辅市警察局局长佩特罗·科亚克也被免职。上述三人被居家监禁。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/181863.html|title=Yanukovych suspends Kyiv City Administration Head Popov and Deputy NSDC Secretary Sivkovych from office, say decrees|publisher=Interfax-Ukraine|date=2013-12-14|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2020-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200907164044/https://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/181863.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://dsb.gzdsw.com/html/2013-12/16/content_245629.htm |title=乌克兰基辅市长遭革职 |newspaper=[[贵州都市报|贵州都市报]] |date=2013-12-16 |accessdate=2014-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413140632/http://dsb.gzdsw.com/html/2013-12/16/content_245629.htm |archive-date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

